{"tid":1929414,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"籲市民勿報警求廁紙 美國警局:你還有樹葉可代替","createTime":"2020-03-17T02:19:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-17T02:25:24.000Z","uid":213167,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"221dd1e4c3325d459f837b0991731ee0d8fef903","tid":1929414,"uid":213167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T02:19:51.000Z","msg":"在<del>新冠肺炎</del> 武漢肺炎 疫情持續的情況下，香港早前出現「廁紙荒」，廁紙成為民眾搶購貨品之一。然而疫情亦在歐美等地蔓延，搶廁紙的情況也在美國出現。美國俄勒岡州紐波特（Newport）近日有民眾買不到廁紙而報警求助。當地警察局周日（15日）在facebook發文，呼籲民眾勿因為沒有廁紙而報警，更提供多種替代品的建議供參考，例如報紙、抹布、廁紙筒等。甚至直言即使沒有警察救助、提供廁紙，「你還是會生存的」。<br />\n<br />\n俄勒岡州紐波特對於要在社交媒體發帖，呼籲民眾勿因沒廁紙而報警也感到難以置信。帖文還非常有心，建議市民若找不到一卷「您喜歡的柔軟，超長毛的兩層橙香味的紙巾，歷史上您仍有很多其他選擇。」例如海員會使用浸在鹽水的舊繩索和錨索、古羅馬人會在一根棍子上用一塊海海綿，也蘸了鹽水、而馬雅人則會用粟米芯等物品擦屁股。貼文中還提醒，他們該地是沿海城市，有大量可用的鹽水，以及貝殼。<br />\n<br />\n貼文續指，現代社會中可代替廁紙的物品不少，例如雜貨店收據、報紙、抹布、棉花球和廁紙筒，甚至提到還有樹葉。早前更有雜誌「Mother Earth News」教人如何用 15 種樹葉做到濕紙巾，如果什麼方法都不行，你還有雜誌內頁。<br />\n<br />\n當地警方強調，廁紙短缺的情况始終會過去，但希望機智一點和耐性一點，「不要打 911 ，我們不會帶廁紙給你」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20200316/_2020031623150699656.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20200316%2F_2020031623150699656.jpg&h=a00ba1ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20200316/_2020031622502727609.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20200316%2F_2020031622502727609.jpg&h=4cb05d63&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n美國民衆搶廁紙。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20200316/_2020031622502889810.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20200316%2F_2020031622502889810.jpg&h=c57c74ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警方指，沒有廁紙還有其他代替品，例如雜誌。"},{"pid":"c41f07cbe4582e35ca929313a8aba783fb525959","tid":1929414,"uid":21545,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T02:20:44.000Z","msg":"要廁紙 報狗做乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"306865bc806dae77b9c8250f5d9aab9ac40ba3cb","tid":1929414,"uid":249979,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T02:22:12.000Z","msg":"美國佬俾左膠縱壞晒"},{"pid":"500e2e3ceec6290fe1ec29eaa82d8c5614332445","tid":1929414,"uid":2757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T02:23:03.000Z","msg":"冇廁紙請用查理斯皇子"},{"pid":"fc8af4f9cef1540719b1a8094c83a316adeecba8","tid":1929414,"uid":166667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T02:23:09.000Z","msg":"仲有左手同右手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81b5da88b3a8fa4877d33c9940a513b281ab441d","tid":1929414,"uid":335434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T02:25:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ftV02bj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FftV02bj.jpg&h=ff7895f1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"718f540e6e751b1c400a50931c42e4f6540da076","tid":1929414,"uid":256142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T02:25:24.000Z","msg":"Be a man, use your hand<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}